data.text: The Haryana Staff Selection Commission (HSSC) will soon release the official notification for the HSSC Group D Recruitment 2023. For the previous recruitment cycle, a total of 18218 vacancies were released for the Group D posts. Candidates who are 10th pass are eligible to apply for the exam. The selected candidates will get a decent pay salary range between Rs. 16900 to Rs. 53500. Candidates who want a successful selection can follow the HSSC Group D Previous Year Papers to get a better understanding of the questions asked in the examination.
